songs.title: PinkPalmTrees
songs.lyrics:
[Speaking]
Hello!
I am [?]
[?]
Welcome to my [?]
[?]
I love my childrens
I love flowers
I love you!

[Instumental]

[Nitty Scott: Speaking]
She does not know her beauty
If she could dance naked under palm trees and see her image in the river, she would know
But there are no plam trees on the street, and dish water gives back no images
-Nina
